# Title: Registry Entries For Azorult Malware
# Author: Trent Liffick
# Date: 2020-05-08
# Level: critical
# Description: Detects the presence of a registry key created during Azorult execution
# MITRE Tactic: Persistence
# Tags: attack.persistence, attack.execution, attack.defense-impairment, attack.t1112
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/registry/registry_event/registry_event_mal_azorult.yml

EventID IN (12, 13) TargetObject="*SYSTEM\\*" TargetObject="*\\services\\localNETService"